{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/ar/media-center/qatar-foundations-thimun-qatar-2019-conference-opens","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"fe75ddb9-7af6-5d1e-b1e4-129ce1de13d3","slug":"qatar-foundations-thimun-qatar-2019-conference-opens","title":"مؤسسة قطر تستضيف مؤتمر ثيمن قطر 2019","date":"2019-01-23","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"6osgodAE6cIuiqSAOQugAs"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"6ab0e079-5e49-5d98-9dde-40a0b247fc78","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>تستضيف مؤسسة قطر النسخة الثامنة من مؤتمر \"ثيمن قطر\"، والذي ينظمة التعليم ما قبل الجامعي بالمؤسسة، في مركز قطر الوطني للمؤتمرات. وسيشهد المؤتمر مشاركة ما يقارب1800  طالب من  64مدرسة محلية ودولية، بهدف تطوير حلول للتحديات الأكثر إلحاحًا في العالم.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"ac5ff799-9155-57ec-9498-6bf2fc6be817","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"d1de2426-ee96-5942-81b5-bc22781d837e","title":"Image1","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":2153,"height":1435}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=560&h=300&q=85 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85 1120w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=1680&h=900&q=85 1680w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7SazkhaNbgvn4GISC/222193c4ffec118bcd647ecaf87755d1/Image1.jpg?w=2153&h=1153&q=85 2153w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/63G8z7S